snippet.title: X-Moon Timelapse - Ludum Dare 25
snippet.description:
I make a game in 48 hours for Ludum Dare 25

Hopefully you do not mind looking at my face the whole time.

Music is soundtrack to the game. You can find the game here: http://www.ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-25/?action=preview&uid=4321
